### Get All Maintenance Companies by Specialization: Elevators (Success)
### During Registration since specialization is the first box.
#Upon selecting the specialization field, It will trigger
#It will trigger this API to fetch all the maintenance companies dealing with that particular spez e.g Elevators
#It will give you both id and company_name
#company name is what you will use to visually present to the user as a drop down menu
# id is what you will use to send to the back-end during signup since it is the primary key.
GET http://localhost:8000/api/maintenance-companies/?specialization=Elevators
Accept: application/json

# Expected Success Response:
# [
#   {
#     "id": 11,
#     "company_name": "Johnson Elevators Co."
#   }
# ]

# Description:
# This test checks if the "Elevators" specialization is correctly returned when requested via query parameters.
# The expected response is a 200 OK status with a list of companies offering the "Elevators" specialization.
# The "id" field will depend on the database values and can vary.

